Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.78,0:00:23.25,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.25,0:00:26.88,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.88,0:00:30.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,As power passes through our clasped hands
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.05,0:00:33.63,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.85,0:00:48.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Working together, let's ride the giant waves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.73,0:00:55.95,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry toward the excitement--\Nthere's the starting signal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.95,0:01:02.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's the time to set sail-- let's raise anchor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.91,0:01:10.04,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut through the rainbow-colored wind\Nand head for a sea of adventure
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:13.51,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be a journey fraught with injury
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.51,0:01:17.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,but what you cherish most will be right there
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.43,0:01:21.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you get into a jam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:24.43,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll always be there to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.43,0:01:28.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right! Now let's move forward
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:32.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,with the sun always in our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.15,0:01:35.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If a storm hits, let's put\Nour arms around each other
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:39.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and gaze at the light beyond
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.66,0:01:43.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,If we gather up the pieces of our dreams
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.37,0:01:46.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they'll make a map leading to tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.66,0:01:49.67,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's grab hold of our wishes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.67,0:01:55.42,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,under the same flag-- together, we're one
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:58.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,One Piece
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how much does it look like it'll cost?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.86,0:02:14.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can pay as much as you like!\NWe've got tons of money!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.99,0:02:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her scars from battle are too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.32,0:02:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you mean it'll take\Nquite a long time to fix her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.82,0:02:23.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Frankly speaking, your ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can no longer be fixed, even with our skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.55,0:02:37.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we've been traveling\Njust fine up until today!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's suppose that we did\Nwhat we could anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.59,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The probability of her\Nreaching the next island is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Merry... Can you really not...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...sail anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.91,0:03:15.04,B1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"Pirate Abduction Incident and a Pirate\NShip That Can Only Await Her End"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.92,0:03:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Sanji. I was so\Nfocused on books that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing you should apologize about.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just assumed that the one\Nwho was with Robin-chan
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,was you in your human form.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.40,0:03:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, who on earth was that masked man?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.07,0:03:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In addition, it's strange that\Nthey suddenly disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.90,0:03:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Robin's scent disappeared there, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope nothing bad happens...\NMy stomach's in a knot...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.66,0:03:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me to take a look at you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This reminds me of what Aokiji said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:03:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did he say something worrisome?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.46,0:04:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said stuff about Robin-chan's past, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he said to us that we'd\Nsomeday regret taking her on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.89,0:04:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.60,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But does that have something to\Ndo with Robin's disappearance?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.31,0:04:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, we're getting nowhere like this.\NLet's go back to the Merry for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's no problem, she'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take us for a spin, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't fix the Merry?! Why not?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you guys amazing shipwrights?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:03.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're worried about money, look!\NWe've got tons!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.53,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you pay, that ship\Ncan't be restored to how she used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm rather impressed that you guys\Nmade it this far in the state she's in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!\NWhat's going on with the Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what a keel is, shameless girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.38,0:05:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shamele...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.93,0:05:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one at the bottom of the ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's the most\Nimportant wood beam on a ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.93,0:05:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It crosses from stem to stern\Nand supports the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you build a ship,\Nyou start off by placing the keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the stem wood, stern wood, frame wood...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...frame brackets and deck beams...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We accurately place all those\Npieces of wood around the keel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how a ship is built.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The keel is the very foundation\Nof a ship's framework.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the essence of the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.67,0:06:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something you can just replace\Nif it takes on a lot of damage...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Replacing the keel is the same\Nas building a ship from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.09,0:06:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So no one can fix her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ship is just a collection of wood\Nthat can only await her end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Don't say it like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not my problem. That's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... Then build a ship from scratch for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.99,0:06:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Build the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coo coo! That's not possible, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.49,0:06:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.83,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can build a similar ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but strictly speaking,\Nno one can build the same ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this world, there are no two\Nships that are exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.29,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.92,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are there any trees in the world\Nthat grow exactly the same way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sailing ships are mostly made of wood,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so the size and curves of the ship are\Nall affected by the shape of the trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.27,0:06:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why an exact duplicate\Nof the ship can't be built,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.02,0:07:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even when using the same blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.94,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For example, even if we build such a ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.57,0:07:09.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,without a doubt, the ones who would\Nfeel that it's a totally different ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.70,0:07:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...would be you guys! Coo coo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.78,0:07:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we really can no longer\Ntravel on the Going Merry?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You either do nothing and wait until she sinks...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or you take her apart quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.92,0:07:29.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.42,0:07:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A caravel!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.42,0:07:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.64,0:07:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! All done! Now the\NGoing Merry pirate ship is all set!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.40,0:07:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... your ship stands on her last legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.36,0:07:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up and buy a new ship here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got money, right?\NI heard that your ship is a caravel.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:08:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To start with, your future journeys will\Nbe tough on such an old-style ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No... I don't intend to get a new ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.00,0:08:04.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.67,0:08:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our ship is the Going Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she's repaired, she can still sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.76,0:08:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine! Today, too,\Nshe sailed here comfortably!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.39,0:08:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet, we're suddenly told\Nthat she can't sail anymore...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can we believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys're saying that because\Nyou don't know how strong she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.36,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be satisfied if you keep\Nsailing on her until she sinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.95,0:08:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you call yourself a ship's captain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.25,0:08:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our discussion is over for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it carefully. If you decide\Nto buy a ship, come again. I'll help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you give us your 300 million, we can\Neven build a state-of-the-art ship for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.21,0:08:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalifa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.30,0:08:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Please give it a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.76,0:08:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a catalogue that contains\Nboth new and used models.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please use it as a price reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Iceberg-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.06,0:09:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone at the gate\Nwho wants to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.44,0:09:10.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any appointment, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that World Government\NOfficial is here again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I turn him away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.57,0:09:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... yeah... Tell him I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you've got quite\Na case of bed head, Lulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops. Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.37,0:09:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I'll ask him to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.92,0:09:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, Iceberg-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys, hide! It's a government official!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.89,0:09:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Hi, Corgy. I'm not around today.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.98,0:09:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I've come all\Nthe way here by sea train.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.11,0:09:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't refuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.45,0:10:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.91,0:10:10.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I somehow detect the scent of pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.92,0:10:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's okay. In any case,\NI want to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.47,0:10:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a child?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.34,0:10:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a fully grown man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.97,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, please don't be so obstinate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a good deal for you today.\NGive me a chance to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.56,0:10:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's go somewhere inconspicuous.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:39.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They keep coming back. How persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What business do they have with Iceberg-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.37,0:10:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with us. It must be\Nsomething to do with power. Coo coo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.62,0:10:47.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I go beat them up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't. They're from the World Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.17,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm...? What? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is something I noticed when I\Ncarried these bags and hid earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are light, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.39,0:11:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't joke like that. Why would they\Nbe light with all that money in them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.24,0:11:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those voices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.12,0:11:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! What's the big fuss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.20,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, woman! If you sit like that...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... There's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.34,0:11:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...no way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.88,0:11:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our 200 million Berries...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.88,0:11:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gone! It's really gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.89,0:11:49.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On closer inspection, they're not our bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What're we gonna do?!\NWh-Wh-Wh-Wh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you guys shouting so loud for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.90,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our money is... gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... totally... gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--What?!\N--Paulie! Did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Are you telling the truth?!\N--Why would I lie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.24,0:12:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that really true?!\N--How noisy... More importantly, Kaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you with the Franky Family earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.96,0:12:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't seen the Franky Family today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.25,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange. I'm sure I saw your long nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a sec, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with the Franky Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.51,0:12:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was with them, or rather,\Nhe was carried away by them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.10,0:12:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's an abduction!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! We'll go look for him right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.48,0:12:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.81,0:12:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Hold on a sec!\NWhere're you gonna look, Luffy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.11,0:12:45.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait, Usopp! Money!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.45,0:12:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where's the Franky Family's hideout?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.58,0:12:56.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's more like a workshop rather than a hideout,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.71,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's at the seashore quite a ways\Nnorthwest from the rocky cape
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.38,0:13:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where your ship is anchored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's called Franky House.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.98,0:13:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.99,0:13:27.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, when there's no way he\Ncould find Usopp all by himself...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no time to look for Luffy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.54,0:13:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better go leave this\Nmoney at the ship for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I march in saying, "Give me our 200\Nmillion back" with 100 million on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be asking them to steal it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.88,0:13:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Yagara-chan, head towards\Nthe bull shop using the shortest route!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna take Zoro and the others\Nwith me and teach them a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Franky Family! Stealing from pirates?!\NYou're the lowest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first floor,\Nthe backstreet shopping district.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.37,0:14:16.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care and have a good day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Yagara-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.05,0:14:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, watch out, lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope... Usopp got away okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.45,0:14:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.24,0:14:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Does anyone know who this guy is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:56.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crowd of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagara-chan! Stop! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...! Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.55,0:15:14.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Usopp! Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.39,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you guys pirates by any chance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Don't stare at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp! Was it the Franky Family\Nwho did this to you? Was it them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Because I'm weak...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.12,0:15:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That large amount of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They stole it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.96,0:15:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't face everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.01,0:16:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally about to have Merry repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel so ashamed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the money.\NWe'll all go and get it back for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.20,0:16:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt quite badly.\NI probably shouldn't move him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.08,0:16:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp, stay here just for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.88,0:16:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hurry back to the ship and bring back help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring Chopper, too, so that he can treat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.76,0:16:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the stolen money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.01,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that their hideout is ahead of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.64,0:16:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll crush them and\Nthat'll be the end of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! This isn't a show!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.27,0:16:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Usopp. Just stay put here, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.94,0:16:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be back right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.32,0:17:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go faster, Yagara-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.20,0:17:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! A runaway bull!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.50,0:17:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were finally about to have Merry repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you pay, that ship\Ncan't be restored to how she used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.18,0:17:23.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we decide to buy a new ship
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.85,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or have someone else manage\Nto fix and improve the Merry,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless we spend all the 300 million\Non the ship to upgrade her,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.53,0:17:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our future journey will certainly be hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.90,0:17:38.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely need that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.62,0:17:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get it back without fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.04,0:17:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.66,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least that's what that shipwright said.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.71,0:17:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This ship...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...can no longer be fixed?\NEven if we pay lots of money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.09,0:17:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... What's gonna happen to Merry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.80,0:17:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.47,0:18:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, it depends on how\NLuffy and the others decide
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after hearing the outcome of the assessment.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.18,0:18:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three at the shipyard will\Nprobably make some decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's too extreme.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.56,0:18:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.77,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's the same old Merry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We and Merry traveled together\Nall the way here from the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.99,0:18:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings can become\Nstronger after each hardship,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.58,0:18:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but ships are different.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.37,0:18:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Their pain only accumulates.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to swallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, what's Usopp\Ngonna say when he hears it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.72,0:18:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love the Merry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We all do. But her scars are so deep\Nthat there's nothing we can do, he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Merry... Robin-chan...\NI'm worried about both.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a restless afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.61,0:18:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Nami's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:05.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Looks like she's alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.66,0:19:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Luffy and Usopp?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami-san! Did something happen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.13,0:19:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yow! Yow, yow! 200 million?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, 200 million!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.64,0:19:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Bro?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.89,0:19:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! You guys are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.27,0:19:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've always wanted that. With this\Nmuch money, we can finally get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.06,0:19:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, didn't we, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.07,0:19:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three years of persevering...\NWe've always said, "If only we could get it..."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.69,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--It was such a long time.\N--Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.07,0:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time we got a chunk of money,\Nwe'd pin our hopes on Yagara races...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.99,0:19:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lose all the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.79,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each time we captured a criminal\Nwith a bounty, we'd party it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.16,0:19:52.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and lose all the money!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:57.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't quite save up the\N200-million-Berry business expense!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.59,0:19:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we finally have it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.51,0:20:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. Good job, you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:08.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, this isn't much,\Nbut here is five million Berries.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.89,0:20:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is to show my appreciation.\NEat and drink as you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.90,0:20:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's our Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.44,0:20:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's party time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.16,0:20:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's trying to defy the Franky Family?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! You're that weak guy from earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You could still stand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me the money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.39,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Give me the money back"? Then are\Nyou one of the Straw Hat's underlings?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.69,0:21:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Bro! Since he's with\NStraw Hat Luffy, I expected him to be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a really strong pirate, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's so weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.45,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.00,0:21:17.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.01,0:21:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.38,0:21:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll admit you've got guts to come\Nto get the money back all by yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.43,0:21:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't let you have it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.31,0:21:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it back to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.64,0:21:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to... have our ship repaired...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.86,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That money is crucial to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.37,0:22:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...we can finally repair the Merry's scars!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.67,0:22:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't let you jerks have it!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.65,0:22:23.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,A piece of a dream that we started grasping
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.07,0:22:26.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Chasing after something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.61,0:22:32.20,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We send our aspirations sailing into the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.20,0:22:34.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when we're exhausted
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.49,0:22:37.66,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We have a compass that can\Nsearch for something constant
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.66,0:22:43.09,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, do you think we can keep it forever?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:46.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,At the end of the dream\Nthat we will reach someday
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We want to be adults as we\Nare now as much as possible
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.97,0:22:51.76,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We pray to this endless sky that we look up at
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.76,0:22:54.85,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:57.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Wild fantasies from our childhood
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.48,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We trace unforgettable memories
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.48,0:23:06.15,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,And try to keep the embers\Nburning that still consume us
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.15,0:23:08.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,To this familiar sunny sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:11.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Together we entrust our feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.78,0:23:14.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,We go beyond the changing time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.37,0:23:19.00,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Eternally... Eternally...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me back...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.13,0:23:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.38,0:23:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me that money back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chopper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.59,0:23:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's hurt very badly, but he'll be okay.\NI can somehow manage to save him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.51,0:23:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Just wait a bit, Usopp.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.43,0:23:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go blow that stupid house away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.77,0:23:43.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.10,0:23:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Rescuing Our Friend!\NRaid on the Franky House"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:49.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
